          p Aliquam sed posuere urna, et gravida nisl. Praesent interdum nisl libero, pretium egestas purus eleifend vitae. Mauris suscipit vel lectus at luctus.        
        form(action="#").application__form
          input(type="text" name="name" placeholder="Your name:" required)
          input(type="tel" name="phone" placeholder="Your phone:" pattern="8[0-9]{10}" required)
          button(type="submit").btn.btn--default ORDER NOW
        .application__warn * Your data will not be transferred

